Why RSJX

ajax/xhr -> async programming

issue with ajax is api call 

every ajax has 3 callback function
      onSuccess
      onFailure
      isCompleted

when we use nested ajax ,it is called as callback hells

So we move to promises 
but promises have certain drawback like 
      not retryable
      not cancellable
      return only one value

RXJS overcome these drawbacks
      retryable
      cancellable
      return stream of value
